Ed Arnold, you're not
even watching Chanel 5.

10
00:01:10,771 --> 00:01:14,575
Loyola Marymount's
playing Portland. I love
this Gathers kid.

11
00:01:14,608 --> 00:01:15,643
What Gathers kid?

12
