He was standing right beyond 
 half-court and all of a sudden 
 he just fell down.

22
00:01:45,173 --> 00:01:48,276
Trainers are all on the court. 
 Hank's mother is rushed on 
 the court.

23
00:01:49,510 --> 00:01:50,844
Lisa, find out where
they've taken him.

24
00:01:50,878 --> 00:01:52,746
I'll send Tommy
and the crew.

25
00:01:52,780 --> 00:01:53,747
You get down there
and help.

26
