882
00:47:58,009 --> 00:47:59,477
You don't know
what you're doing.
Oh, and you do?

883
00:47:59,510 --> 00:48:01,646
Uh-huh. When I finish
my career in the NBA,

884
00:48:01,679 --> 00:48:04,215
