in broadcasting.

885
00:48:04,249 --> 00:48:05,951
Good evening,
ladies and gentlemen,

886
00:48:05,984 --> 00:48:08,419
Our very special guest
this evening is that

887
00:48:08,453 --> 00:48:11,489
