00:49:26,431 --> 00:49:28,766
They wanna win,
that's what I want,
that's what I'm gonna do.

910
00:49:28,799 --> 00:49:30,735
Oh, you are,
are you?
Uh-huh.

911
00:49:30,768 --> 00:49:33,504
Hm, I guess you're gonna be
one of the lucky ones, huh?

912
00:49:33,538 --> 00:49:37,975
[LAUGHS] Luck's
got nothing
to do with it.

913
00:49:42,213 --> 00:49:44,082
[CROWD CHEERING]

