okay, right?

991
00:53:49,794 --> 00:53:52,763
I mean, it's no big deal.
It's gonna be okay, right?

992
00:53:52,797 --> 00:53:53,864
Right?

993
00:53:53,898 --> 00:53:55,232
I didn't say that.

994
00:53:55,900 --> 00:53:57,968
